        two transit events. Using the best quality data set, we were
        able to yield 20 narrowband transit light curves, with each
        passband spanning a 20 nm wide interval. After removal of all
        systematic noise signals and light curve modeling, the
        uncertainties for the resulting radius ratios lie between 337
        and 972 ppm. The radius ratios show little variation with
